name: Completed Work Orders
query:
SELECT
  `tabWork Order`.name as "Work Order:Link/Work Order:160",
  `tabWork Order`.creation as "Date:Date:140",
  `tabWork Order`.production_item as "Item:Link/Item:100",
  `tabWork Order`.item_name as "Item Name:Link/Item:180",
  `tabWork Order`.qty as "To Produce:Int:70",
  `tabWork Order`.produced_qty as "Produced:Int:70",
(select total_cost from `tabBOM` where name = `tabWork Order`.bom_no) as "COP:Float:100"
FROM
  `tabWork Order`
WHERE
  `tabWork Order`.docstatus=1
  AND ifnull(`tabWork Order`.produced_qty,0) = `tabWork Order`.qty
